{"tid":1358585,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《全民頭盔運動》","createTime":"2019-07-24T03:13:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T06:25:06.000Z","uid":241763,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fc4e57bf7142ff73fa76978baa3bd41f478ac8eb","tid":1358585,"uid":241763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:13:46.000Z","msg":"全民頭盔運動！<br />\n黎緊會發夢既朋友更加必須帶備，唔好以為你唔係最前線唔會衝就唔需要<br />\n<br />\n第一：經過721元朗事件，冇去遊行既普通市民都比人打到爆晒缸，我地要保護自己安全，而保護頭部係最緊要。<br />\n<br />\n第二：出黎遊行既朋友，唔理你係和理非定勇武，全民頭盔可以引起社會關注，甚至係國際關注。<br />\n<br />\n我地要比個訊息：我地係香港連出街都會擔心自身安全，呢個源自於警察濫權，政府、警隊既無能，無能力控制黑幫暴力，令所有市民陷入恐懼，我地對警隊同埋政府撤抵失去信心！"},{"pid":"9a7435d4adc4b7b8fe3da3e6a60d8af5be3479dd","tid":1358585,"uid":273252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:17:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i7VU37d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi7VU37d.png&h=37389333&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uxp3jDL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuxp3jDL.jpg&h=75ce7be0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[抗議警黑合作] 全民港鐵戴頭盔 全民出街戴頭盔 日常<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1363165\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1363165</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">舊post 全民頭盔月<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aagrbhU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aagrbhU</a></span>"},{"pid":"fd2be02ba43ba22b7a7af2cd46c9c573d51b3e8a","tid":1358585,"uid":171860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:19:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cd0dd4bb88a34f3e8817154c16c6b1f6dcb952b","tid":1358585,"uid":278922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:25:06.000Z","msg":"搵人設計一個潮流頭盔義賣，又可以幫到眾籌。一舉兩得"}]}